entries.femaleVariant: I told him – Kostya, don't take anything out of Leningrad. And guess what happen? They catch him at the border, ass crammed with drugs.
You know how kids are. Hasn't seen his pops in twenty years. Prolly just wanted to impress you.
Oh, he impressed me, all right – with his fucking stupidity. Now we'll have to find someone else for the job...
